oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Postcard accordion of Camp Mills, Long Island, N.Y.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Color postcard accordion showing views of Camp Mills, Long Island, N. Y. The object is addressed to "R.M. Massey/Carthage, Tenn./Smith Co./Route 6." Pvt. Adron Hershell Massey served in Co. E, 150th Inf. Regt., 38th Div. He sent this packet to his family. He was from Defeated, Smith County, Tenn. and was born in May, 1895. His unit never deployed overseas and he was discharged from service in June, 1919.
